{"tid":300937,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無小提琴柚可以救救我隻尾指?","createTime":"2017-06-28T09:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T03:31:25.000Z","uid":117929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72447b70ee5dead52d7fc59851e803bf745c3ed4","tid":300937,"uid":117929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"小弟今年30歲, 學左小提琴都斷斷續續有差唔多一年...<br />\n就係一直搞唔掂隻尾指...<br />\n個問題係...<br />\n一按到第4指時隻尾指就會好似抽筋咁僵直左,<br />\n第二關節鎖死左...<br />\n只能夠僵直住咁按絃...<br />\n唔能夠變番曲住尾指咁按絃...<br />\n網上話依種尾指好似係因為double joint 既問題...<br />\n你地以前學琴有無遇到依個問題...<br />\n有無辦法/方法可以改善都依個問題...<br />\n我好灰心...天生隻尾指咁樣練緊都有依個問題...<br />\n唔通我天生就唔可以學好小提琴...T^T<br />\n有無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個情況就好似咁樣...(網上google圖片)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/174907_cd6810d1ed29fc25149b652f48063f6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F174907_cd6810d1ed29fc25149b652f48063f6a.jpg&h=9ec3f4cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54650f1846add34b9b9d95e98d9228627f86134c","tid":300937,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"轉出d 隻手，而家有d 似死力"},{"pid":"552953b094c2a1d0d9d94b838608f7cbe52c11fd","tid":300937,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"手腕扭多d?"},{"pid":"8c3b90b686758606740a7e4813dc5a8d9dd057cd","tid":300937,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"試下禁尾指時 隻無名指唔好離開曬指版得唔得？<br />\nBtw放放鬆啲隻手"},{"pid":"51f95182e0e6a04d67f545addb15d4e66374242a","tid":300937,"uid":18827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"放鬆隻手，左手唔洗太用力<br />\n試下尾指㩒落右手手掌，力道大概係㩒到右手手有小小白，唔好死力去㩒"},{"pid":"b5e7217c720a37e29fa65197b2f6d8bc3ecaf353","tid":300937,"uid":53953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"練琴前放鬆下手，fing 下，每隻手指做少少伸展。<br />\n拉個陣多d 保留手指 1 2 3 4 4 3 2 1 咁拉下<br />\n左手手腕唔夠放鬆，太崩緊同埋要扭右少少。<br />\n如果做到試下開始練34 既trill"},{"pid":"cac78dcdf0ca25d834656d95d34f0ce41c4b8b65","tid":300937,"uid":46967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"其實keep 住咁 之後會有咩問題?<br />\n利申 唔係玩提琴"},{"pid":"d85e19a8f13001eb4db7a9f5a3637fbf8c587279","tid":300937,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"搵我學<br />\n<br />\n利申： 小提琴 LT"},{"pid":"91d2060d781ae4762ffebc5eb30be5f91c07b80e","tid":300937,"uid":53953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵我學<br />\n<br />\n利申： 小提琴 LT</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nop 問下野就要搵你學，就咁打句LT 以為自己好撚勁？"},{"pid":"fead077e6b5a129545767f5e0fc573ec9c2edb3d","tid":300937,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵我學<br />\n<br />\n利申： 小提琴 LT</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nop 問下野就要搵你學，就咁打句LT 以為自己好撚勁？</blockquote><br />\n勁就唔勁既 出面教緊收bu價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你覺得有個LT好勁？ 利申下又要比你屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主 想交流乜pm下我囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af16fc140801532abc0bc26a64a0e855199f5c08","tid":300937,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"第一. 隻手指尾唔洗壓咁低 會更加無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  盡量用指尖部份 頭3隻手指壓實唔郁 不斷用 3 4 3 4 開拍子機 可以開112=1拍 （最快208）（八個半拍對四分四）由G線綀上E線 不斷重複 分弓綀一次 連弓綀一次 綀熟可以試下全連弓 一弓過八個半拍 （G 3 4 3 4 3 4 3 4），短時間應該有改善<